title: freshii
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. International fast food chain eatery where you can customize wraps, bowls, and salads. Choose from many kinds of vegetables plus there is brown rice and a grilled tofu protein option. Has smoothies and juices. Small shop with a few tables.
